text: Taichung Blue Whale is a Taiwanese women's football club based in Taichung. Founded in 2014, it is associated with National Taiwan University of Sport. The team currently competes in the country's top-tier women's domestic competition, the Taiwan Mulan Football League. ==Players== ===Current squad=== ==Honours== *Taiwan Mulan Football League **Champions (3): 2017, 2018, 2019 ==References== ==External links== * Category:Association football clubs established in 2014 Category:Football clubs in Taiwan Category:Sport in Taichung Category:2014 establishments in Taiwan Category:Taiwan Mulan Football League
